onMouseOut="nd();">42</A>
Caesar, as praetor, assumed office January 1, 62 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN>, the day after Cicero laid down the <SPAN CLASS="whole">consul</SPAN>&shy;ship; but the new tribunes for the year 62 assumed office early in December of 63.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
