	<HR CLASS="endnotes"><A ID="endnotes_T"></A>
	<H2>
Thayer's Notes:
	</H2>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note:Scaurus_or_Catulus" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Cicero*.html#ref:Scaurus_or_Catulus
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">a</A>
Swollen Ankles or Puppy, respectively.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note:Sestius" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Cicero*.html#ref:Sestius
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">b</A>
Professor John D. Morgan writes to correct the Loeb text here: even if <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">Sextius</SPAN> is commonly seen for this man, properly it's <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">Sestius</SPAN>; and sure enough, for the same gentilicium, Bernadotte Perrin, the Loeb translator of all these <I>Lives</I>, will give the latter form elsewhere
	<A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Brutus*.html#4.3
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,0,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
(<I>Brutus</I>, 4.3)</A>.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="a0 justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note:Astura" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Cicero*.html#ref:Astura
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">c</A>
An elegant sea resort in Roman times, mentioned also as an imperial retreat by Suetonius (<A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Suetonius/12Caesars/Augustus*.html#97.3.2
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,0,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();"><I>Aug.</I> 97.3</A>,
	<A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Suetonius/12Caesars/Tiberius*.html#72.2.2
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,0,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
<I>Tib.</I> 72.2</A>). It was heavily fortified in the 12c and is now the small town of Torre Astura in Latina province: it is about 15 km SE of Anzio (<SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">Antium</SPAN>) by road. See for example
	<P CLASS="b0 center">
	<A HREF="
http://www.mondimedievali.net/Castelli/Lazio/roma/nettuno.htm
	"TARGET="offsite"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,2,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
Mondi Medievali
	</A>
•
	<A HREF="
http://www.frcoulter.com/pics/02-16-03/02-16-03.html
	"TARGET="offsite"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,2,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
Fr. Gary Coulter's site
	</A>



